Some fighting game ports (Super Street Fighter series, IIRC) did not scale down the graphics. Instead they kept the original graphics and panned around the screen as needed, making the characters take up proportionally more of the screen.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3706">qbradq</a> — Sat May 14, 2011 6:05 pm</p><hr />
